Images: ["[630_360_16803...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/thumb_files/630_360_1680351934-336.jpg)", "[1680351934-21...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680351934-217.jpg)"]

