Images: ["[630_360_16803...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/thumb_files/630_360_1680345536-171.jpg)", "[1680345537-39...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680345537-394.jpg)"]

